Metadata.name: Сircle of Hell
Metadata.desc: Follow the arrows and keep right. Warning - oncoming traffic! Good luck!

Metadata.name: Beach Bum
Metadata.desc: Off-road track at Vespucci Beach. Blazers or Bifta for atmosphere, Desert Raid & Trophy Truck for win. No Dunes. GTA for pits ;) 1 lap = 80s.

Metadata.name: Magic Square
Metadata.desc: A race just for fun =) Choose an even number of laps for even more fun.

Metadata.name: Fire! Fire! Fire!
Metadata.desc: The race in hot desert with fire! Enjoy! Stunt 50%.

Metadata.name: Blue Storm
Metadata.desc: Blue&purple race in a yellow desert. Select 2 or 4 laps.

Metadata.name: Great Maze Bank
Metadata.desc: The exciting Maze Bank tour. Not bad at night. Do not use RE-7B.

Metadata.name: Infinite Ocean
Metadata.desc: Race track in the form of eight. Recommended amount of laps is 4+. There is also a pitlane in GTA mode.

Metadata.name: Cemetery Morning
Metadata.desc: A typical morning at the Los Santos cemetery. Deathmatch mainly on pistoles. With Easter eggs! =)

Metadata.name: Grapeseed Duel
Metadata.desc: Recreated track from PS4, creator - Evil_Tuinhek. You must choose an even amount of laps since they are not equal in terms of length. Good luck ;)

Metadata.name: Docks Aura
Metadata.desc: Very tight and tricky track in LS docks. It is originally created for coupes. Pitlane in GTA mode. Supers = weird choice. Beta version.

Metadata.name: Sniper Challenge (new)
Metadata.desc: Kill as many as possible and win this challenge.
